# Hangman Code

```
  validity = False
  while validity == False:
    letter = input('Enter a letter')
    for x in "qwertyuiopasdfghjklzxcvbnm":
      if letter == x and len(letter) > 0 and len(letter) < 2:
        validity = True
      
      if validity == True:
        return letter
     
 
 ```
